00:15:59,224 --> 00:16:00,183
check it a bit?

385
00:16:02,104 --> 00:16:03,184
N-No need.

386
00:16:03,264 --> 00:16:04,303
Thank you.

387
00:16:16,967 --> 00:16:19,640
(Happy Cake Shop)

