516
00:21:14,423 --> 00:21:16,624
I'll get it to your car after work.

517
00:21:18,024 --> 00:21:18,824
Come on.

518
00:21:19,304 --> 00:21:20,263
What are you doing?

519
00:21:20,663 --> 00:21:21,903
