534
00:21:50,584 --> 00:21:51,663
You are the best.

535
00:21:51,983 --> 00:21:53,544
Are you happy to hang out with me?

536
00:21:53,624 --> 00:21:55,064
Yeah, I'm so happy.

537
00:21:56,864 --> 00:21:58,103
You're so happy?

538
00:21:58,183 --> 00:22:00,103
