565
00:22:37,743 --> 00:22:38,784
Everything is ready.

566
00:22:38,864 --> 00:22:39,984
You can move in anytime.

567
00:22:40,064 --> 00:22:40,824
Okay?

568
00:22:47,144 --> 00:22:48,024
Xu Kaixin.

569
00:22:50,104 --> 00:22:50,823
A-Are you crazy?

570
00:22:50,903 --> 00:22:51,623
You've become

571
00:22:51,703 --> 00:22:53,304
